Class Enquiry

java.lang.Object
Enquiry
public class Enquiry extends Object
Enquiry class This class is used to create an enquiry object. Enquiry objects are used to store information about an enquiry. Attributes: sender, message, enquiryID, response, responder and campName Constructors: Enquiry(String sender, String message, String campName, int enquiryID) Enquiry(String sender, String message, int enquiryID, String response, String responder, String campName) It also contains getters and setters for all the attributes.
Since:
2023-11-24
Version:
1.0
